title.narrative: OUTPUT 8.1:PLANNING & EMERG COORDINATION

description.narrative: Output 8.1: By 2019, internal efficiency and effectiveness of programme planning and coordination enhanced, which contributes to Cross-Sectoral Monitoring, Data And Situation Analyses, Cross-Sectoral Planning And Programme Reviews. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Outcome 8: By 2019, National and sub-national capacity on evidence based planning, and management enhanced to emphasis on children and women's disparities across sectors.
